OL,4,CWastewater is 'polluting rivers with
OL,5,Cmicroplastic'
OL,6, Untreated wastewater "routinely
OL,7, released into UK rivers" is creating
OL,8, microplastic hotspots on riverbeds.
OL,10,FThat is the conclusion of a study in
OL,11,FGreater Manchester, which revealed high
OL,12,Fconcentrations of plastic immediately
OL,13,Fdownstream of treatment works.
OL,15,FThe team behind the research concluded:
OL,16,Funtreated wastewater was the "key
OL,17,Fsource" of plastic pollution.
OL,19,FThe water company that operates along
OL,20,Fthe river the scientists studied said
OL,21,Fit didn't "fully accept" the findings.
